The following IDL programs are used to construct forcing data

1) forcing_tollgate.pro
   converts ASCII station data to a NetCDF file

2) make_monthly_forcing.pro
   construct serially-complete monthly forcing data

3) stn_exposure.pro
   computes the exposure of all stations

4) plot_stn2grid_monthly.pro
   makes monthly maps of climate variables

5) make_gridded_timeseries.pro
   makes the gridded hourly timeseries

6) plot_interp_timeseries.pro
   plots the interpolated hourly time series
